    "description": {
      "value": "<em>Replace this with a proper description.</em>\n<details>\n<summary>Credits and Instructions</summary>\n<h2>Made by Elwin</h2>\nBased on Bakana and Xenophes version.\n <h3>Requires:</h3>\n<ul>\n   <li>Elwin Helpers (Enable in Settings)</li>\n   <li>Times-up</li>\n   <li>Active Token Effects</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Optionals:</h3>\n<ul>\n   <li>Sequencer (to support star motes animations)</li>\n   <li>JB2A (free or patreon) (to support star motes animations)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Usage:</strong></p>\n<p>This spell needs to be used to activate. It creates animations of star motes around the caster (if Sequencer is avaialble) \nand allows to make a special attack with a star mote which removes one mote each time. When no star mote remains the spell is ended.</p></details>",
